    <td class="welcome" align="left"><br /><h1>Welcome to Hind Tools</h1><br />
	 Established in the year 1988 at Nashik, 140km. from Mumbai, the financial capital of India, Hind Tools is an engineering and financially stable manufacturing organisation offering high quality global solutions with over 400 dedicated workforce to support all your sheet metal needs .<br />
We at Hind Tools handle low to high volume production quantities and offer a comprehansive range of services starting with complete product design with a prototype division, along with high quality tool manufacturing through precision sheet metal fabrication, to value added assemblies and direct end customer order fulfillment.<br /> 
Hind Tools provides engineering based, cost effective customer focused solutions for precision steet metal parts and value added assembly, through innovation and excellence in execution, always exceeding customers expectations.</td>
